<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</h1>
    <p>
      I'm reaching out for help because of the skill(s) you listed on your Volunteerly profile. 
      <ul>
      <% @user.skills.each do |skill| %>
      <li><%= skill.name %></li>
      <% end %> 
      </ul>

      I'd love to organize a time to share our skills. <br>
    </p>
    <p><%= link_to('Check out my Volunteerly profile', users_url(@user.id), method: :patch) %>. Also feel free to contact me directly at <%= @sender.email %></p>
    <p>Note: You may have to sign in to your Volunteerly account to view my profile first.</p>

    <p>I can't wait to hear from you.</p>
    <p>-- <%= @sender.name %></p>
  </body>
</html>